ğŸ”¹ What is Scaffolding?

Scaffolding is the process of automatically generating files and folders

It creates a ready-to-use project structure

Saves development time

ğŸ“Œ The concept of scaffolding was originally introduced by:

Ruby / Ruby on Rails

