node_modules
  - Contains all installed dependency files

public
  - Contains static resources (images, documents, icons)

src
  - Contains dynamic resources (React components, logic)

eslint.config.js
  - JavaScript code quality & linting rules

package-lock.json
  - Dependency lock file (used in production, should not be modified)

README.md
  - Project documentation written by developers

vite.config.js
  - Vite bundler configuration file

index.html
  - Application startup (entry) page

