ğŸ§  Key Points to Remember (Interview / Exam)

Vite is a fast modern bundler

Bundlers use scaffolding

index.html is the entry point

main.jsx connects React to the DOM

React uses Virtual DOM for performance

React 19 recommends function components

createRoot() is mandatory in React 18+

